Terrorists are looking to destroy an area where government lab equipment has been scattered around an old Ancient Ruins Research Group setup. And Counter-Terrorists have been tasked with keeping those materials safe.

A defuse map based on gameplay, and nade use. I'm not the best at making maps look good... Unfortunately I couldn't make the radar. Please provide feedback. i plan on heavily modifying parts of this map.
